question: Tī chit ê lōe-iông lia̍t-toaⁿ lāi, ūi-tiāⁿ tō-ián ū siōng-chē ê chè-chok (chē-tō-ián mā sǹg chāi-lāi)?
Tī Geoff Cawthorn ch directed ê chhut-phín tiong, 'No. in season' ê pêⁿ-kūi siáⁿ-mih?

Annette Moore siat ê kái-bo̍k ê miâ, hiah-ê chiah ū siōng koân ê 'No. in series' ? (Annette Moore siat ê kái-bo̍k ê miâ, hiah-ê chiah ū siōng koân ê 'Tè-lia̍t hō', ū siá Annette Moore ê siá ê kái-bo̍k, sī siá ê sè-liè ti̍t ti̍t-ti̍t ê siōng koân ê hō ê kái-bo̍k ê miâ?)
Guan-îⁿ 1999 nî 6 goe̍h ê pò͘-chhut ji̍t-tîm, cháiⁿ-iáⁿ chhut-phín ê huiⁿ-pò͘ hêng-thài.
answer: 1999 nî 6 goe̍h ê tiān-sì-kio̍k ê pò͘-chhut sī chi̍t-ê kó͘-tēng ê lé-pài chi̍t-pái ê pò͘-chhut. Pò͘-chhut ji̍t-tîm sī 6 goe̍h 1 hō, 8 hō, 15 hō, 22 hō, kap 29 hō, múi chi̍t kang lóng sī keh 7 kang, chí-chāi chi̍t ê sin tiān-sì-kio̍k lóng sī teh lé-pài ê chi̍t-ê bêng-khak ê ji̍t-tîm pò͘-chhut.

question: Liệt chhit 'Robert Klenner' chí-tō ê hit-ê chhit-phín ê miâ-chheng, in chāi 1999 nî ê tē-2 kuì (4 goe̍h 1 ji̍t kàu 6 goe̍h 30 ji̍t) tiong pò͘-chhut.
Tī lia̍t-chhut ê kio̍k-tiāu lāi-té, ū choán-chí tōa-sò͘ ê phiah ū siáng hō-chòe Catherine Roden chòe-ê tō sī chòe-ê?

Nāi-ia̍h sê-lia̍t ê tē-30 hō kàu tē-40 hō ê lóng-chóng chi̍p-chio̍h, nā-chún sū-ba̍t siū-tó chi̍t-ê 'No. in series' hō-liâu, i sī siū-tó ke-thiⁿ 100 hō siōng-tōa, kin-á-ji̍t tòe ê miâ ū '"Everyone Loves a Winner"' chit-ê chi̍p-chio̍h, siá chòe sin ê 'No. in series' ài ū siá-chòe siáⁿ-chē?
Tī chitê kài-sû lāi-bīn, ū-khó-lêng ū chi̍t-ê chāi-chāi ha̍p-chok ê tō-ián hām chok-ka Louise Crane-Bowes? Nā-sī ū, chhiáⁿ lia̍t chhut hit-ê tō-ián ê miâ.
answer: Ū--ê, tō-ián Peter Fisk hām chok-ka Louise Crane-Bowes ū chi̍t-ê chāi-chāi ê ha̍p-chok. In chòe-hóe chòe-chòe ê chi̍t-phìⁿ sī "The Human Touch" hām "Friends and Lovers". Koh-ū, tō-ián Robert Klenner hām Louise Crane-Bowes mā ha̍p-chok koè "Truth and Consequences (Part 2)", tān-sī Peter Fisk ū nn̄g pái ha̍p-chok, tō khah chē-khah chē.

question: Tī "Directed by" hām "Written by" nn̄gê khong lâi-oân, siánn-mi̍h ê khong ū khèng chē chē lâng chham-ú (chiū-sī chhiau-kòe 1 lâng miâ-toaⁿ)?
Tsiah-tsiah ài kā jîn-bu̍t ê chhut-ián sòaⁿ-sōe hō͘-chòe tē, hô-hô͘ ê chi̍t chi̍p ê 'Chē-lia̍t-tiâu' ê sò͘-ba̍k ūi-tio̍h chha-khoah siōng-tōa ê khang-khò, che chi̍p ê āu-chi̍t chi̍p sī-mí?
Pai Peter Fisk chn 1999 nî 3 goe̍h hō͘ chòe ê chiat-bo̍k ū siáⁿ-mih?
